svg.title: Roadmap to the Unicode BMP
svg.desc: This chart is a roadmap of character allocation for Unicode plane 0: Basic Multilingual Plane (BMP). It was created on 2024-09-11 using Unicode 16.0 data. Characters are categorized more-or-less by the chapters in The Unicode Standard.
